msgstr "Krita 的色彩取樣器工具參考。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:17
msgid "Color Sampler Tool"
msgstr "色彩取樣器工具"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:20
msgid ""
"This tool allows you to choose a point from the canvas and make the color of "
"that point the active foreground color. When a painting or drawing tool is "
"selected the Color Sampler tool can also be quickly accessed by pressing "
"the :kbd:`Ctrl` key."
msgstr "色彩取樣器可以從畫布中採樣顏色並設定成前景色。在使用繪圖工具時\\ :kbd:`Ctrl`\\ 鍵是快捷鍵。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:24
msgid ""
"There are several options shown in the :guilabel:`Tool Options` docker when "
"the :guilabel:`Color Sampler` tool is active:"
msgstr "在使用色彩取樣器時工具選項裡會有數項設定："

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:26
msgid ""
"The first drop-down box allows you to select whether you want to sample from "
"all visible layers or only the active layer. You can choose to have your "
"selection update the current foreground color, to be added into a color "
"palette, or to do both."
msgstr ""
"第一個下拉式選單能設定圖層的採樣，分別是採樣全部可見圖層和採樣目前圖層。而下面的兩個選項則分別設定色彩採樣的生效地方，一個是更新前景色，一個是加入到調色板"
"，兩者可以同時生效。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:30
msgid ""
"The tool has been renamed and is now consistently called the *Color Sampler "
"Tool*. (Beforehand it was non-consistently referred to as either *Color "
"Picker* or *Color Selector*)"
msgstr "現在已經更名為*色彩取樣器*。（在這版本之前的名字是*選色器*。）"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:34
msgid ""
"The middle section contains a few properties that change how the Color "
"Sampler picks up color; you can set a :guilabel:`Radius`, which will average "
"the colors in the area around the cursor, and you can now also set a :"
"guilabel:`Blend` percentage, which controls how much color is \"soaked up\" "
"and mixed in with your current color. Read :ref:`mixing_colors` for "
"information about how the Color Sampler's blend option can be used as a tool "
"for off-canvas color mixing."
msgstr ""
"新增了一些改變色彩取樣器採樣方式的選項；現在可以設定\\ :guilabel:`半徑`\\ ，這將會取範圍內顏色的平均值，同時透過設定\\ "
":guilabel:`混色`\\ 控制吸取並混合至目前顏色的比例。參閱\\ :ref:`mixing_colors`\\ "
"以取得色彩取樣器的混色選項如何在畫布外進行混色的資訊。"

#: ../../reference_manual/tools/color_sampler.rst:36
msgid ""
"At the very bottom is the Info Box, which displays per-channel data about "
"your most recently picked color. Color data can be shown as 8-bit numbers or "
"percentages."
msgstr "在最下方的的是資訊欄，能夠顯示最近採樣顏色的每個通道的資訊。色彩資訊能被顯示成 8-bit 數值或是百分比。"

